                            <p></p><div style="text-align: center;">

<h2>GLORIOUS VICTORIES</h2>

<p></p></div><br />
 Defeats after defeats have been pounding the AAF Regime. The freedom fighters had made considerable progress in their struggle against tyranny...<br />
 After the participation of Sgt. Nelson and T/5 Zim, Officer Hill himself parachuted into Altis to review the situation and provide high-level tactical advice to the rag-tag band of rebels, accompanying him were the Recon marksmen of the European attachment of Charlie Company: PFC Danberg and PFC Milo; along with an another jungle warfare expert Pvt. Lewis<br />
<img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160612012712_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" /><br />
<img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160611005103_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" />

<p>With their assistance, the rebels had managed to fend off 2 large AAF assault into their base of operation and made considerable progress in upgrading the equipment for future fights: for the first time, an FIA Convoy confidently patrol <br />
the roads of Altis!!!</p>

<p><img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160612015704_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" /><br />
<img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160612013227_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" /></p>

<p>PFC Milo and PFC Danberg provided immeasurable marksmanship during skirmishes with the Puppet Regime and had brought terror right into the heart of the Imperialist CSAT Forces!</p>

<p>Our day culminated in an all-out assault on the AAF airfield that PFC Burkardt and I had failed to conduct, with preliminary plan made by the genius tactical mind of Officer Hill and PFC Burkardt's amazing leadership which resulted in a crushing defeat for the AAF forces: here's a picture of me using NATO-provided guided missile on an AAF infantry squad with devastating effect<br />
<img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160612030510_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" /></p>

<p>The day ended with the freedom fighters holding onto the towns of Oreokastro, Abderra and the Abderra Airport, establishing a functioning FIA-controlled area with guaranteed human rights and democracy</p>

<p><img src="http://i1202.photobucket.com/albums/bb366/thomashung1/107410_20160612035037_1_1.png" alt="enter image description here" title="enter image title here" /></p>

<p>WE WILL FIGHT, AND WE WILL BE VICTORIOUS!<br />
EVER FORWARD</p>
