                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message userContent">
                            <h3>Information Regarding:Antistasi Play Times!!!</h3>

<p>SO in case you were wondering when and how to join us during our modern day crusades of guns, guts, and glory. Feel free to drop on in the Team speak and Company server each week on:</p>

<p>Fridays: 8pm - 11pm EDT<br />
Saturdays: 9am - 12pm EDT (For those euro folk out there <img class="emoji" src="../../resources/emoji/lol.png" title=":D" alt=":D" height="20" /> ) <strong>We will likely run Saturday afternoon as well</strong></p>

<p><strong>We Currently use the 29th Mods (AKA the mods we use for drills)</strong></p>

<p>These times are simple rough outlines of when we start and end. Add either myself of PFC Thomas for real time updates on when we begin and the excitement that is sure to follow.</p>

<h3>In other News!</h3>

<p>Antistasi developers have just launched their first official public tests of their newest addition to the scenario!<br />
<strong>Full RHS integration</strong><br />
Including full replacement of infantry, weapons, and vehicles! So no more Thermals on the pesky roadblock static MGs <img class="emoji" src="../../resources/emoji/wink.png" title=";)" alt=";)" height="20" /></p>

<p>Hope to see you there! Even if only for only a little while. No prep needed so drop in/out is fully supported. <br />
As always AIT restrictions apply and 29th standards are to be held up. 29th server. 29th Rules.</p>

<p>Cheers Gents!<br />
See you on the other side.</p>
